Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Briga* me za to što drugi ljudi misle o meni. (I don't care about what other people think about me.)
2. *Briga* te za moj život, nemoj se miješati. (It's none of your business what I do with my life, don't interfere.)
3. On ne vodi *brigu* o svojim finansijama. (He doesn't take care of his finances.)
4. Molim te, *brini* se o svom zdravlju. (Please take care of your health.)
5. Moja majka uvijek *brine* o meni, čak i kada sam odrasla. (My mother always worries about me, even though I'm an adult.)
6. Niko ne želi da *brine* o ovom problemu. (Nobody wants to deal with this problem.)
7. Treba da *se brinemo* o našoj planeti i zaštitimo je od zagađenja. (We should take care of our planet and protect it from pollution.)
8. Ona je *brinula* o svom bolesnom ocu dok nije ozdravio. (She took care of her sick father until he got better.)
9. *Brigu* o organizaciji proslave preuzela je moja prijateljica. (My friend took care of the organization of the party.)
10. Kada se budeš osjećala usamljeno, znaj da imaš nekoga ko *brine* za tebe. (When you feel lonely, know that there is someone who cares about you.)

(Note: The word "brigu" in the examples above is used in various forms and positions, as requested. The translations are provided in parentheses after each sentence.)